data.description: Great Hutto home near schools, restaurants and retail. Three spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms with the Primary suite on the main level. Open floor plan between kitchen, dining and family room downstairs, plus a large flex space/office/playroom upstairs. Huge backyard with extended covered patio. Roof is two years old! No HOA!
